<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Activate Your Account</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h2 {
      color: #333;
    }
    p {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .code-box {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #fff;
      background-color: #007bff;
      padding: 10px;
      display: inline-block;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #999;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Activate Your Account</h2>
    <p>Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
    <p>Thank you for signing up. Here is your activation code:</p>
    <div class="code-box">{{activationCode}}</div>
    <p>Please enter this code in our system to activate your account.</p>
    <p>If you did not sign up, please ignore this email.</p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2025 NestJS Company. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>Powered by NestJS ðŸš€</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
